{"tid":1404030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府：激進示威者目無法紀 挑戰國家主權 予以強烈譴責","createTime":"2019-08-04T02:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T05:42:07.000Z","uid":212626,"like":14,"dislike":367,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"81c427f722fa3cc7d2d65a900b638f8da75b2ddc","tid":1404030,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:02:15.000Z","msg":"政府回應油尖旺區示威活動<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  政府發言人就昨天（八月三日）在油尖旺區的示威活動作以下回應：<br />\n<br />\n  雖然警方經與主辦方協商後已就在大角咀舉行的遊行發出不反對通知書，但有示威者在遊行開始後旋即偏離原定路線，堵塞油尖旺區一帶多條主要道路，更一度堵塞紅磡海底隧道出入口，對附近一帶的交通、商業活動及市民日常生活造成嚴重影響。有關行為不但違法，更罔顧公共秩序及其他市民的需要，我們深表遺憾。<span style=\"color: red;\">事實上，近日以表達訴求為名的示威活動，涉及的違法及堵路行為變本加厲，遠超文明社會可接受的言論自由。</span><br />\n <br />\n  示威活動期間再次出現暴力行為，有部分激進示威者暴力衝擊警署、破壞汽車、多處縱火等。此外，懷疑有示威者刻意破壞國旗，觸犯《國旗及國徽條例》。<span style=\"color: red;\">政府對於激進示威者目無法紀，蓄意破壞社會安寧，甚至挑戰國家主權，予以強烈譴責。警方會嚴正執法，而使用暴力的違法示威者亦應受法律制裁。 <br />\n </span><br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月4日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間0時23分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/04/P2019080400020.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F04%2FP2019080400020.htm&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USN5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=5135c298\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/04/P2019080400020.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8148bd5db06ffa28ae9803ba32e983f9c277ae0e","tid":1404030,"uid":78971,"like":348,"dislike":1,"score":347,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:04:17.000Z","msg":"已經冇人想理呢啲千篇一律嘅發言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係就立即回應五大訴求<br />\n唔係咩都唔洗傾"},{"pid":"0a10f0f666caf6e687721159b1c81c41578505be","tid":1404030,"uid":111951,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:04:37.000Z","msg":"聽日罷工，去七區集會既人全部入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1403977\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1403977</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2bce4c64583c25f4b6206d1d0db21119aaef13d9","tid":1404030,"uid":188176,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:04:46.000Z","msg":"根本無人會睇"},{"pid":"b449fab04057840e1d2105bdc48ccd859e3b1192","tid":1404030,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e66585ec989869e1f9fa01e964bc58906a9b6e","tid":1404030,"uid":9570,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:29:35.000Z","msg":"其實仲有人理佢地點講？"},{"pid":"307898052fc74fd165fb0b5ec62e37e865dcfe20","tid":1404030,"uid":288670,"like":75,"dislike":3,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:31:02.000Z","msg":"今次咁撚樣都唔暴動？"},{"pid":"7d795016bb064c3ce95841aeb67a79bfaadbe156","tid":1404030,"uid":142965,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:31:20.000Z","msg":"係咪喺口交部度copy番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0c1ed6dd180b7da75c5fb4e67fcc0b3eb7f1fc","tid":1404030,"uid":164372,"like":110,"dislike":0,"score":110,"quote":{"pid":"307898052fc74fd165fb0b5ec62e37e865dcfe20","tid":1404030,"uid":288670,"like":75,"dislike":3,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:31:02.000Z","msg":"今次咁撚樣都唔暴動？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:31:21.000Z","msg":"尖沙咀警署啲車冇得賠"},{"pid":"16332148ec3ea292d862905bd72984f7eaa7e2a0","tid":1404030,"uid":44171,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:31:51.000Z","msg":"主權？邊個俾佢？有冇問過我地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dee2dc9df83cf42a2f084c97782b1b9ce5cbd442","tid":1404030,"uid":202137,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:32:36.000Z","msg":"如果塊布無跌落海係咪唔會有反應？"},{"pid":"8440c7570a80782966b6572caabb1e2e495093a3","tid":1404030,"uid":219813,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:33:00.000Z","msg":"連記者會都唔開 打點廢話就算"},{"pid":"6d1e3d2986677f69eb968159ccb1eb3726f17405","tid":1404030,"uid":68199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:33:25.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"a9b71b16e288993d1aa37518a2d9b17a0b84fa8e","tid":1404030,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:33:36.000Z","msg":"haha"},{"pid":"5fc494bad51f67aa601093a0786682bf0434db79","tid":1404030,"uid":42090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:34:46.000Z","msg":"bababa<br />\nwfc"},{"pid":"d854563506a8e1407121cc42897bf7d8a7a56336","tid":1404030,"uid":102491,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:36:27.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死垃圾黑警<br />\n憑咩冇學歷冇技能冇責任心冇腦冇使命感冇獨立思考冇大冇細冇EQ仲學人警黑合作<br />\n憑咩拎3萬幾人工仲話有宿舍排 含撚啦你地<br />\n諗住自己惡晒 番工攞正牌打人唔帶證開槍 你老母臭閪你係濕鳩公僕黎 係我地既僕人黎架 你啲死人糧濕鳩盾爛鳩槍係我地交稅買 你係咁用黎射鳩番我地<br />\n帶住槍捉白衫話好驚要調頭走 你老母閪打好市民就1挑100都唔驚<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母臭閪死黑警等天收生仔冇屎忽生女一世做雞老母老婆日日俾人中出 冇人監管天會收你地"},{"pid":"57912629f8c938adb4b90b033962b5fb9f6c4a6d","tid":1404030,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":14,"score":-14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:37:22.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n求下你地青年人 唔好再玩火 香港唔值得要你地禁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不玩火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[Be fire, my foe] 攬炒戰術？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nx22GfM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2