ke":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:15:59.000Z","msg":"五大訴求都講到口臭 <br />\n政府唔口臭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fd4c1cfa80334fcb2269397aa6f41fa5cfa056","tid":1404030,"uid":143701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:17:49.000Z","msg":"其實無咩特別事都唔洗出稿啦 一係五大訴求 放返義士 一係攬炒"},{"pid":"dad38f774eb417fb53cb54b17b3d6513a46ebceb","tid":1404030,"uid":268342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:17:52.000Z","msg":"除左個日子，全部見過，下次改個日子，成篇可以用返.....頂幾十萬人工真好做"},{"pid":"50a3d0ae309165f3db5473e4fac1e166b5d4287c","tid":1404030,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:18:33.000Z","msg":"政權除了要我們恐懼多，還要散佈仇恨。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065677&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USN5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=76b1421c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1065677&h=892f01aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1065677</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。」（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n「藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。」（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）<br />\n<br />\n「沒有舞蹈的革命，是不值得發動的革命。」（A revolution without dancing is a revolution not worth having）<br />\n<br />\n「面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。」（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n「我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地裡，我們是自由的。」（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n「力量來自團結，團結來自信念」（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n「恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。」（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n「就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿著強大的力量。」（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)"},{"pid":"cf7263009848d0aecfb68adf9a8188d4315a26f7","tid":1404030,"uid":29283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:25:25.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗share 依啲垃圾文 次次都一樣架啦"},{"pid":"a6ad5d3806ad6095b9998b3985cfcc4faf864f72","tid":1404030,"uid":205825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:28:16.000Z","msg":"吹撚到 衝擊國家主權"},{"pid":"2dcaa39a28e1ea3aeff759d10163282317d8c0a2","tid":1404030,"uid":213246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:30:24.000Z","msg":"好啦 明啦 收皮啦你"},{"pid":"998f831d42e49660221c1ed32bb4e96813362ee1","tid":1404030,"uid":4838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:34:54.000Z","msg":"69就強烈譴責<br />\n搞到而家做咩都係強烈譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲啲有狗比人屠都係強烈譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9f6c58170720baa9e9c8441ba5476e1a2201c8","tid":1404030,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307c40719de0f417caebfb49c6ab6ee4b2ac1632","tid":1404030,"uid":152976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:55:05.000Z","msg":"是撚但喇"},{"pid":"b8406229506ec93495ffa48dfc0d054bb87eb2af","tid":1404030,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"998f831d42e49660221c1ed32bb4e96813362ee1","tid":1404030,"uid":4838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:34:54.000Z","msg":"69就強烈譴責<br />\n搞到而家做咩都係強烈譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲啲有狗比人屠都係強烈譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:05:54.000Z","m